        <description>The Department of War has been focusing on enhancing mental health support for its Airmen, while the Coast Guard rescued a stranded man on Lake Huron. The National Biodeterrence Efforts report highlights China&#39;s increasing focus on biosciences as part of its national security strategy. Joint Task Force Southern Border marks one year of success in bolstering southern border security through integrated operations.</description>
